<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="156">Supplemental description of female genitalia.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="156">Ovipositor simple: gonostylus with a long apical seta, distinctly longer than wide; distal gonocoxites elongated (Fig. 9b). Spermatheca connected in medial portion of vagina (Fig. 9b).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
